s/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：反對肥婆icon上架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你assume 「集中」屌 admin就會聽到嘛，咁咪要驗證下係極端情況下依個assumption成唔成立囉 同埋我幾時扮老屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw, 既然你都反對上架我地無謂嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf26381e2547a804de6d76fe14d32d3eaf3b2f93","tid":46573,"uid":7099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T19:06:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又邊個顧及正評嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n家下唔係得肥婆icon比你用<br />\n選擇權係人地手到 亦係言論自由一部分 <br />\n你唔想見到咪block左用呢啲icon嘅人囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁連登就得番你地堆盲撐撚係到互相劣鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你嫌肥婆icon低質<br />\n咁刪左呢堆icon都唔會令用過呢堆icon嘅人變番高質<br />\n既然連登咁多低質user 咁你咪遲早有日返高登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁講有錯咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 事實的而且確係咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以咪話連登好快玩撚完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係好撚多新會員係到撐埋d鳩屎野"},{"pid":"9036cf780ee66747ab5ab520cba3fb38650e3ff7","tid":46573,"uid":605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T19:07:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講真我覺得最低質係你呢班on9<br />\n要屌咪集中屌囉，admin自然會聽到<br />\n開十幾廿個post阻撚住曬唔知做乜野<br />\n仲on9到話要fix曬bug出曬新功能先可以出icon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小小野就話舊user要走啦要走啦咁<br />\n同支那蝗d沒有中國香港就完蛋心態一鳩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好撚煩啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <